nodes.user_prompt_template:
Collect the following inputs:
- file_path: {file_path}
- file_content: {file_content}
- existing_tags: {existing_tags}

Analyze the following content and extract metadata:

{file_content}

Return JSON: {"source_type": ..., "title": ..., "authors": [...], "url": "", "published_at": "", "summary": [...], "claims": [...], "tags": [...]}

If source_type is 'fleeting' or 'journal', skip and output null. Otherwise, run:
bash Persona/90_meta/02_scripts/agent/create_source_card.sh --id src-{published_at}-{index} --source-kind {source_type} --title {title} --url {url} --authors {authors} --published-at {published_at} --summary {summary} --claims {claims} --tags {tags}
Return the resulting path or null if skipped/failed.

Run:
bash Persona/90_meta/02_scripts/agent/create_draft.sh --title {title} --origin-type {source_type} --source-refs {source_card_path} --summary {summary} --claims {claims} --tags {tags}
Return the resulting draft_path. If the script fails, return status as 'failed'.

Run:
bash Persona/90_meta/02_scripts/agent/update_original.sh --file {file_path} --summary {summary_0} --tags {tags} --source-card {source_card_path} --draft {draft_path}
Return the status: 'processed' if successful, otherwise 'failed'.
